You can simply ask Alexa to control your device. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Cheego Smart" app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our "Cheego Smart" app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search "Cheego Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable "Cheego Smart" skill, and you'll be navigated to "Cheego Smart" login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:

Alexa, dim the bathroom light.
Alexa, set the bedroom light to fifty percent.

Alexa, turn on light on the DEVICENAME.
Alexa, is light on on DEVICENAME?

Alexa, what is the environmentalHumidity on the DEVICENAME
Alexa, what is the temperature of DEVICENAME

Alexa, set the volume of the DEVICENAME to 50
Alexa, turn the volume down on the DEVICENAME by 20.
Alexa, turn the volume down on DEVICENAME

Alexa, show me the DEVICENAME
Alexa, talk to DEVICENAME

Alexa, what is the brightness on DEVICENAME
